  <div class="ProfileHeaderCard">
  <h1 class="ProfileHeaderCard-name">
    <a href="/RebeccaGeach" class="ProfileHeaderCard-nameLink u-textInheritColor js-nav">Rebecca Geach</a>

  <h2 class="ProfileHeaderCard-screenname u-inlineBlock u-dir" dir="ltr">
    <a class="ProfileHeaderCard-screennameLink u-linkComplex js-nav" href="/RebeccaGeach">
      <span class="username u-dir" dir="ltr">@<b class="u-linkComplex-target">RebeccaGeach</b></span>
    </a>
  </h2>

  

      <p class="ProfileHeaderCard-bio u-dir" dir="ltr">Spelthorne CLP Secretary and Spelthorne Labour PPC 2015 &amp; 2017. Fabian Women's Network mentee. Views are my own.</p>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Rebecca Geach Retweeted Jeremy Corbyn</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Homelessness shame on the doorsteps of Government<a href="https://t.co/Ct7LFdGa6L" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/status/963789632885444608" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/status/963789632885444608"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/jeremycorbyn/s</span><span class="invisible">tatus/963789632885444608</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Rebecca Geach added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">
    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/jeremycorbyn/status/963789632885444608" data-conversation-id="963789632885444608" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>
    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="963789632885444608" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="jeremycorbyn" data-user-id="117777690" href="/jeremycorbyn/status/963789632885444608" data-conversation-id="963789632885444608" tabindex="0">
      <div class="tweet-content">
        <div class="QuoteTweet-authorAndText u-alignTop">
            
  <div class="QuoteTweet-originalAuthor u-cf u-textTruncate stream-item-header account-group js-user-profile-link">
    <b class="QuoteTweet-fullname u-linkComplex-target">Jeremy Corbyn</b><span class="UserBadges"><span class="Icon Icon--verified"><span class="u-hiddenVisually">Verified account</span></span></span><span class="UserNameBreak"></span><span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>jeremycorbyn</b></span>
  </div>

          
          
          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">I've just been told about the death of a rough sleeper right by the entrance to Parliament. The powerful can't carry on walking by on the other side while people don't have a home to call their own. It's time all MPs took up this moral challenge and properly housed everyone.</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Been out on the <a href="/hashtag/LabourDoorstep?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>LabourDoorstep</b></a>?         <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Embed Tweet</button>

  </ul>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">.<a href="/nomiprins" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="25187182"><s>@</s><b>nomiprins</b></a> Right. As former tax counsel to world's largest bank, the hardest thing we had to do was pay some taxes. Paying zero was easy.</p>
</div>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">The founder of ARM says Hammond and May wrong to be thrilled that it is being bought by Japanese giant SoftBank<a href="https://t.co/NyyvpLG2Eo" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/hermannhauser/status/755008815553273858" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/hermannhauser/status/755008815553273858"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/hermannhauser/</span><span class="invisible">status/755008815553273858</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Robert Peston added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">
    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/hermannhauser/status/755008815553273858" data-conversation-id="755008815553273858" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>
    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="755008815553273858" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="hermannhauser" data-user-id="39096276" href="/hermannhauser/status/755008815553273858" data-conversation-id="755008815553273858" tabindex="0">
      <div class="tweet-content">
        <div class="QuoteTweet-authorAndText u-alignTop">
            
  <div class="QuoteTweet-originalAuthor u-cf u-textTruncate stream-item-header account-group js-user-profile-link">
    <b class="QuoteTweet-fullname u-linkComplex-target">Hermann Hauser</b><span class="UserBadges"></span><span class="UserNameBreak"></span><span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>hermannhauser</b></span>
  </div>

          
          
          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">ARM is the proudest achievement of my life. The proposed sale to SoftBank is a sad day for me and for technology in Britain.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

        <button type="button" class="dropdown-link">Copy link to Tweet</button>

  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="0">Thinking of those suffering <a href="/hashtag/WorldRefugeeDay?src=hash" data-query-source="hashtag_click" class="twitter-hashtag pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr"><s>#</s><b>WorldRefugeeDay</b></a>. May the world help Syrians fleeing conflict rather than condemn them.</p>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Yvette Cooper Retweeted Harry Harpham MP</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Terribly sorry to hear the sad news about Harry Harpham, a big loss to Sheffield. Thoughts with all family &amp; friends<a href="https://t.co/vhekchL6j3" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/harry4bh/status/695385052440428545" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/harry4bh/status/695385052440428545"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/harry4bh/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/695385052440428545</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Yvette Cooper added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">
    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/Harry4BH/status/695385052440428545" data-conversation-id="695385052440428545" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>
    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="695385052440428545" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="Harry4BH" data-user-id="3001662514" href="/Harry4BH/status/695385052440428545" data-conversation-id="695385052440428545" tabindex="0">

        <div class="QuoteTweet-authorAndText u-alignTop">
